      "date": "2016-05-03 13:35:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nThe reason for realloc was to simplify the code. With malloc you need to do a initial call and then in case of the overflow call malloc again. This way one have only one call point. The first time realloc is called it behaves the same as malloc.",
